Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.90,1:32:40.10,*Default,440,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(700,378)\fad(700,400)\fs16}とほかみゑみため
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.90,1:32:40.10,*Default,440,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(700,400)\fs16}远神恵赐
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.22,1:32:59.85,*Default,441,0,0,0,,在那艘船里出现了吧
